=== Linux ===
this was tested on Ubuntu 16.04.

to create a stream from the webcam:

	./run

to watch the stream:
	1. Open VLC player
	2. In the menu bar select "Media"
	3. Inside "Media" select "Open Network Stream..."
	4. in the Network tab enter this URL:
		udp://@:2000
	5. Click the "Play" botton in the bottom

=== Windows ===
1. install ffmpeg
2. run stream.bat
3. run play.bat
